## This repository accompanies the manuscripts: 
## Byungwook Choi, Peter Tiffin
## Department of Plant and Microbial Biology, University of Minnesota

## For ALL Raw datasets 
## Dataset List included:
- Data_readcounts.csv: Raw read counts from dual-seq transcriptome profiles in this study
- Data_TPM.csv: Gene-level expression profiles (TPM) across entire libraries
- Data_TPM_cdlg: Gene-level expression profiles (TPM/codinglength) across entirhe libraries
- Data_Log2TPM.csv: Gene-level expression profiles (Log2(TPM+1)) across entirhe libraries
